d345061a-3d37-4f01-aed5-a240b488e528.title: Eve Online
d345061a-3d37-4f01-aed5-a240b488e528.summary: EVE Online is a free-to-play community driven space MMO where players can choose their own path from countless different options. Experience space exploration, immense PvP and PvE battles, mining, industry and a thriving player economy in an ever-expanding sandbox.

49823120-cfa1-41aa-9da7-62c6bd8f091a.title: Satisfactory
49823120-cfa1-41aa-9da7-62c6bd8f091a.summary: Satisfactory is a first-person open-world factory building game with a dash of exploration and combat. Play alone or with friends, explore an alien planet, create multi-story factories, and enter conveyor belt heaven!
